text: Květa Fialová (1 September 1929 – 26 September 2017) was a Czech actress. She was best known for her performance in Lemonade Joe. She was born in Veľké Dravce, Czechoslovakia. She also appeared in Dinner for Adele (1977) and I Enjoy the World With You (1982). Fialová died in Prague, Czech Republic on 26 September 2017 at the age of 88.Actress Květa Fialová passes away at 88 ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1929 births Category:2017 deaths Category:Czech movie actors Category:Czech television actors
